    "## 4. Creación y activación de entornos\n",
    "\n",
    "### Métodos principales para crear entornos virtuales:\n",
    "\n",
    "#### **Método 1: venv (Recomendado para principiantes)**\n",
    "\n",
    "    # Crear entorno virtual\n",
    "    python -m venv nombre_entorno\n",
    "\n",
    "    # Activar (Windows)\n",
    "    nombre_entorno\\Scripts\\activate\n",
    "\n",
    "    # Activar (Linux/Mac)\n",
    "    source nombre_entorno/bin/activate\n",
    "\n",
    "    # Desactivar\n",
    "    deactivate\n",
    "\n",
    "#### **Método 2: conda (Para ciencia de datos)**\n",
    "\n",
    "    # Crear entorno con conda\n",
    "    conda create -n mi_entorno python=3.11\n",
    "\n",
    "    # Activar\n",
    "    conda activate mi_entorno\n",
    "\n",
    "    # Desactivar\n",
    "    conda deactivate"
