    "## 7. Buenas prácticas profesionales\n",
    "\n",
    "### Principios fundamentales:\n",
    "\n",
    "#### **1. Un entorno por proyecto**\n",
    "\n",
    "    BIEN:\n",
    "    proyecto_a/\n",
    "      ├── venv_a/\n",
    "      └── requirements.txt\n",
    "    proyecto_b/  \n",
    "      ├── venv_b/\n",
    "      └── requirements.txt\n",
    "\n",
    "    MAL:\n",
    "    Un solo entorno global para todos los proyectos\n",
    "\n",
    "#### **2. Nunca instalar en el entorno base**\n",
    "\n",
    "    MAL: pip install pandas  # En entorno base\n",
    "    BIEN: pip install pandas  # Dentro de entorno virtual activado\n",
    "\n",
    "#### **3. Versionar requirements.txt, no el entorno**\n",
    "\n",
    "    Incluir en Git: requirements.txt, requirements-dev.txt\n",
    "    NO incluir en Git: venv/, __pycache__/, .env"
